::Battera::

She arrived at the Cybertron Fire. She landed a quarter of a mile 
away so the autoguns wouldn't fire on her.  She walked very slowly 
towards the ship. She kept a wary eye out for anybots who might be on 
patrol.  She waited to see if any bots walked by her.
